id: "class:investigator#malice_binder"
name: "Malice Binder"
description: "A lock of hair, a bit of blood, even a footprint is enough to grant\
  \ a wily witch hunter an edge. Malice binders often rise from the ranks of the common\
  \ folk rather than from wealthy nobles or the church. Their magic is old and crude,\
  \ but devastatingly effective against those they hunt."
modifications:
